libshapedraw.internal
Class LSDController

java.lang.Object
  libshapedraw.internal.LSDController

public class LSDController
extends Object

Internal singleton controller class, lazily instantiated. Relies on a bootstrapper (mod_LibShapeDraw) to feed it Minecraft game events.
